          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Protecting Indian Tribes from Scams Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Trade Commission (FTC), after consultation with Indian tribes, to report on unfair or deceptive practices that target tribes or tribal members. The FTC must submit such report to Congress and make it publicly available. Further, the FTC must update its website to include information for consumers and businesses on identifying and avoiding unfair or deceptive practices that target tribes or tribal members.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2020-08-28T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
